<br />
<br />- Load the two name tables on startup
<br />- In the NMI-loop, increase scrolling on each keypress, and check if the scroll value is 255. If yes, load the third name table (from PRG-ROM) into $2000. Scroll again, and check if scroll value is 255. If yes, load the fourth name table into $2400. 
